msgstr "Preferéncias calendièr Orage"

#: plugin/org.xfce.orage-settings.desktop.in:14 org.xfce.orage.desktop.in:15
msgid "calendar;date;schedule;appointment;time;"
msgstr "calendièr;calendari;data;rendètz-vos;ora;temps;agenda;"

#: org.xfce.orage.appdata.xml.in:11
msgid ""
"Orage aims to be a fast and easy to use graphical calendar. It uses portable"
" ical format and includes common calendar features like repeating "
"appointments and multiple alarming possibilities."
msgstr ""
"Orage a per objectiu d'èsser un calendièr grafic rapid e facil d'utilizar. "
"Utiliza lo format ical portable e compren de foncionalitats comunas de "
"calendièr coma los eveniments repetitius e de possibilitats multiplas "
"d'alarmas."

#: org.xfce.orage.appdata.xml.in:15
msgid ""
"Orage does not have group calendar features, but can only be used for single"
" user. It takes a list of files for ical files that should be imported. "
"Contents of those files are read and converted into Orage, but those files "
"are left untouched."
msgstr ""
"Orage a pas de foncionalitats d'agenda de grop, mas pòt èsser utilizat "
"solament per un utilizaire unic. Requerís una lista de fichièrs per los "
"fichièrs ical que deurián èsser importats. Lo contengut d'aqueles fichièrs "
"es legit e convertit en Orage, mas aqueles fichièrs son daissats intactes."

